Trade/Device Name(s): Nano-CheckTM AMI 3 IN 1 Cardiac Marker Test cTnl, CK-MB and Myoglobin
Regulation Name(s): Creatine phosphokinase/creatine kinase or isoenzymes test system
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Nano-Check AMI 3 IN 1 Cardiac Marker Test for qualitative detection of cTnI, CK-MB, and Myoglobin using immunochromatographic cassette format.
Indications for Use Summary: Qualitative, rapid immunoassay for cTnI, CK-MB, and Myoglobin in human serum and plasma, as an aid in the diagnosis of acute myocardial infarction (AMI).
